## 🎨 Design System

This document establishes UI standards and design patterns for the application.

---

## Principles

1. **Consistency** - Same pattern throughout the application
2. **Accessibility** - Sufficient contrast for readability (WCAG AA)
3. **Responsive** - Mobile-first approach
4. **Performance** - Smooth transitions (200ms)

