## Button Styles

### Primary Buttons

**Use:** Main actions, CTAs

#### Tailwind CSS
```tsx
className="bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-200"
```

#### Bootstrap
```tsx
className="btn btn-primary"
```

#### Material UI
```tsx
<Button variant="contained" color="primary">
```

#### React Native
```tsx
style={{ backgroundColor: colors.primary, padding: 12, borderRadius: 8 }}
```

**States:**
- Default: `bg-primary`
- Hover: `bg-primary/90` (10% lighter)
- Active: `bg-primary/80` (20% lighter)
- Disabled: `opacity-50`

---

### Secondary Buttons

**Use:** Secondary actions, cancel, "Back"

#### Tailwind CSS
```tsx
className="border border-border-strong text-text-secondary hover:bg-bg-subtle hover:text-text-primary transition-all duration-200"
```

#### Bootstrap
```tsx
className="btn btn-outline-secondary"
```

#### Material UI
```tsx
<Button variant="outlined" color="secondary">
```

**States:**
- Default: `border text-secondary`
- Hover: `bg-bg-subtle text-primary`
- Active: `bg-bg-subtle/80`
- Disabled: `opacity-50`

---

### Ghost Buttons

**Use:** Minimal actions, icons

#### Tailwind CSS
```tsx
className="text-text-secondary hover:bg-bg-subtle hover:text-text-primary transition-all duration-200"
```

#### Material UI
```tsx
<Button variant="text">
```

---

### Destructive Buttons

**Use:** Delete, logout, dangerous actions

#### Tailwind CSS
```tsx
className="bg-error text-white hover:bg-error/90 transition-all duration-200"
```

---

## Transitions

All transitions should use:
```css
transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out
```

**Exceptions:**
- Loading states: `transition-opacity duration-150`
- Modal/Popover: `transition-transform duration-300`
- Page transitions: `transition-opacity duration-300`

---

## Accessibility

### Minimum Contrast

- **Text on background:** WCAG AA (4.5:1)
- **Icons:** WCAG AA (3:1)
- **Hover states:** Maintain minimum contrast

### Focus States

All interactive elements should have:

#### Tailwind CSS
```tsx
className="focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
```

#### CSS
```css
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--primary);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

---

## Responsive Design

### Breakpoints

| Name | Min Width | Target |
|------|-----------|--------|
| `sm` | 640px | Mobile landscape |
| `md` | 768px | Tablet |
| `lg` | 1024px | Desktop |
| `xl` | 1280px | Large desktop |
| `2xl` | 1536px | Extra large |

### Mobile-First Approach

```tsx
// Start with mobile styles, then add breakpoints
<div className="p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8">
  {/* Content */}
</div>
```

