## Anti-Patterns (DO NOT USE)

```tsx
// ❌ Black hover (too dark)
className="hover:bg-black"

// ❌ No transition
className="bg-primary hover:bg-blue-500"

// ❌ Too many color changes
className="hover:text-red-500 hover:bg-yellow-200"

// ❌ Very slow transition
className="transition-all duration-1000"

// ❌ Inconsistent hover states
className="hover:scale-110"  // Only on some buttons
```

